Package ca.team4308.absolutelib.control

Class XBoxWrapper

java.lang.Object
ca.team4308.absolutelib.control.XBoxWrapper
public class XBoxWrapper extends Object
Wrapper class for Xbox controller functionality in FRC. Provides easy access to buttons and analog inputs.
